#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Fixed** root certificate rotation in Citadel to reuse values from the "
"expiring root certificate into the new root certificate (`Issue 19644 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/19644>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:15
msgid "**Fixed** telemetry to ignore forwarded attributes at the gateway."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Fixed** sidecar injection into pods with containers that export no port"
" (`Issue 18594 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/18594>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Added** telemetry support for pod names containing periods (`Issue "
"19015 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/19015>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Added** support for generating ``PKCS#8`` private keys in Citadel agent"
" (`Issue 19948 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/19948>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:25
msgid "Minor enhancements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Improved** injection template to fully specify ``securityContext``, "
"allowing ``PodSecurityPolicies`` to properly validate injected "
"deployments (`Issue 17318 "
"<https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/17318>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:31
msgid "**Added** support for setting the ``lifecycle`` for proxy containers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:32
msgid ""
"**Added** support for setting the Mesh UID in the Stackdriver Mixer "
"adapter (`Issue 17952 <https://github.com/istio/istio/issues/17952>`_)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:37
msgid "Security update"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:39
msgid ""
"`ISTIO-SECURITY-2020-002 </news/security/istio-security-2020-002>`_ Mixer"
" policy check bypass caused by improperly accepting certain request "
"headers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/1.3.x/announcing-1.3.7/index.rst:43
msgid ""
"`CVE-2020-8843 <https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-"
"bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2020-8843>`_: Under certain circumstances it is "
"possible to bypass a specifically configured Mixer policy. Istio-proxy "
"accepts ``x-istio-attributes`` header at ingress that can be used to "
"affect policy decisions when Mixer policy selectively applies to source "
"equal to ingress. Istio 1.3 to 1.3.6 is vulnerable."
msgstr ""

